commit 7293a51033b630ae2e36d28c926c36f4fb5ccdd8
Author: Kerem Kat <katkerem@amazon.com>
Date:   Fri Feb 28 15:50:36 2025 +0000

    Use dlopen/dlclose instead of dl_iterate_phdr.
    
    Using dlopen/dlclose during symbol parsing  ensures a library is loaded and
    keep it from being unloaded during parsing.

